1
00:00:10,028 --> 00:00:12,530
Haru voice over: <i>( gasps )</i>
<i>WHAT WAS THAT LAG ABOUT?</i>

2
00:00:14,563 --> 00:00:17,463
<i>HOLD ON! THIS IS</i>
<i>A BACK DOOR PROGRAM!</i>

3
00:00:21,063 --> 00:00:22,496
<i>WAIT...</i>

4
00:00:22,496 --> 00:00:23,930
<i>WHOEVER DID THIS IS</i>
<i>PROBABLY WATCHING</i>

5
00:00:23,930 --> 00:00:25,630
<i>WHAT I’M DOING RIGHT NOW.</i>

6
00:00:25,630 --> 00:00:28,430
<i>FOR THE TIME BEING, THE BEST</i>
<i>THING FOR ME TO DO IS NOTHING.</i>

7
00:00:28,430 --> 00:00:30,063
<i>PRETEND LIKE I NEVER NOTICED.</i>

8
00:00:30,063 --> 00:00:31,196
( sighs )

9
00:00:34,230 --> 00:00:37,630
Chiyuri voice over:
<i>HEY, HARU...</i>

10
00:00:37,630 --> 00:00:43,363
<i>IF KUROYUKIHIME CAN GIVE YOU</i>
<i>WHAT YOU WANT. HELP YOU CHANGE.</i>

11
00:00:43,363 --> 00:00:45,330
<i>THEN I WON’T GET</i>
<i>IN THE WAY.</i>

12
00:00:45,330 --> 00:00:48,663
<i>BUT PLEASE.</i>
<i>STOP LETTING</i>
<i>HER BOSS YOU AROUND.</i>

13
00:00:48,663 --> 00:00:50,296
( grunts )

14
00:00:50,296 --> 00:00:53,030
<i>IF YOU CAN BE</i>
<i>HER BOYFRIEND,</i>
<i>THEN DO IT.</i>

15
00:00:53,030 --> 00:00:54,963
<i>YOU’LL SHOCK</i>
<i>THE ENTIRE SCHOOL.</i>

16
00:00:54,963 --> 00:00:57,930
<i>IT’LL BLOW</i>
<i>THEIR MINDS.</i>

17
00:00:57,930 --> 00:01:01,763
OKAY, THANKS...
CHIYU.

18
00:01:05,096 --> 00:01:07,363
♪

19
00:02:38,698 --> 00:02:41,598
ALL RIGHT. SEE YA.

20
00:02:41,598 --> 00:02:43,198
( gasps )

21
00:02:43,198 --> 00:02:46,531
HEY. MY MOM’S
NOT HERE TODAY.

22
00:02:46,531 --> 00:02:48,765
NO! STOP!
THIS IS WRONG!

23
00:02:48,765 --> 00:02:50,165
Kuroyukihime:
MIND IF I JOIN?

24
00:02:50,165 --> 00:02:51,198
AAH!

25
00:02:51,198 --> 00:02:53,031
SO, HARUYUKI.

26
00:02:53,031 --> 00:02:56,231
WHAT DO YOU SAY WE THREE
REACH A NEW LEVEL TOGETHER?

27
00:02:56,231 --> 00:02:58,965
AAH!

28
00:02:58,965 --> 00:03:00,365
AAH!

29
00:03:00,365 --> 00:03:02,831
( panting )

30
00:03:06,031 --> 00:03:09,965
( sobs )
I’M SO GONNA BURN IN HELL.

31
00:03:14,165 --> 00:03:18,165
I’M SO ASHAMED.
OH, I’M PATHETIC.

32
00:03:18,165 --> 00:03:19,831
IF I HADN’T CABLE-LINKED
WITH CHIYU,

33
00:03:19,831 --> 00:03:21,331
I NEVER WOULD’VE
HAD THAT DREAM!

34
00:03:21,331 --> 00:03:23,031
Kuroyukihime:
GOOD MORNING,
YOUNG MAN.

35
00:03:23,031 --> 00:03:24,198
AAH!

36
00:03:24,198 --> 00:03:25,398
INTERESTING.

37
00:03:25,398 --> 00:03:27,031
THIS HOW YOU
ALWAYS GREET
PEOPLE?

38
00:03:27,031 --> 00:03:28,598
NO! OF COURSE NOT!

39
00:03:28,598 --> 00:03:31,398
G-GOOD MORNING.
HOW ARE YOU?!

40
00:03:31,398 --> 00:03:32,731
MM...

41
00:03:32,731 --> 00:03:35,431
LISTEN...
BY THE WAY...

42
00:03:35,431 --> 00:03:37,531
ABOUT YESTERDAY...

43
00:03:37,531 --> 00:03:38,998
I APOLOGIZE.

44
00:03:38,998 --> 00:03:40,565
I BEHAVED
IMMATURELY.

45
00:03:40,565 --> 00:03:43,765
AAH! NO!
I’M THE ONE
WHO’S SORRY.

46
00:03:43,765 --> 00:03:46,031
I DIDN’T MEAN
TO HAVE THAT DREAM.

47
00:03:46,031 --> 00:03:46,831
WHAT DREAM?

48
00:03:46,831 --> 00:03:48,798
NOTHING!
NOT THE DREAM!

49
00:03:48,798 --> 00:03:51,431
I MEANT, FOR LEAVING
WITHOUT SAYING GOODBYE.

50
00:03:51,431 --> 00:03:53,365
THAT WAS RUDE.
( chuckles )

51
00:03:53,365 --> 00:03:54,898
I DON’T BLAME YOU.

52
00:03:54,898 --> 00:03:57,398
AFTER ALL,
FIRST I ACCUSED
YOUR BEST FRIEND.

53
00:03:57,398 --> 00:04:00,598
AND THEN I TASKED YOU
WITH A CHALLENGE THAT
WAS SURELY IMPOSSIBLE:

54
00:04:00,598 --> 00:04:02,365
GETTING HER
TO CABLE-LINK
WITH YOU.

55
00:04:02,365 --> 00:04:05,531
UH, ACTUALLY...
I GOT HER TO DO IT.

56
00:04:05,531 --> 00:04:06,531
DO WHAT?

57
00:04:06,531 --> 00:04:08,965
WE CABLE-LINKED.

58
00:04:13,231 --> 00:04:14,231
WHERE WAS THIS?

59
00:04:14,231 --> 00:04:17,031
IT WAS...
AT HER HOUSE.

60
00:04:17,031 --> 00:04:18,565
IN WHICH ROOM?

61
00:04:18,565 --> 00:04:21,331
WELL, WE WERE IN HER...
BEDROOM.

62
00:04:21,331 --> 00:04:22,931
OH?

63
00:04:22,931 --> 00:04:24,898
I WAS ABLE TO HACK IN
AND CHECK HER MEMORY
FOR ANY EVIDENCE--

64
00:04:24,898 --> 00:04:26,665
AND HOW LONG
WAS THIS CABLE?

65
00:04:26,665 --> 00:04:29,798
UH...
THIRTY CENTIMETERS...
OR SO.

66
00:04:29,798 --> 00:04:31,031
HMM!

67
00:04:34,165 --> 00:04:37,565
( gasping, panting )

68
00:04:37,565 --> 00:04:41,565
( school bell chiming )

69
00:04:41,565 --> 00:04:44,131
Haru voice over: <i>WHY DID SHE</i>
<i>JUST STORM OFF LIKE THAT?</i>

70
00:04:44,131 --> 00:04:45,531
( sighs )

71
00:04:45,531 --> 00:04:46,965
<i>I NEED TO TALK TO HER.</i>

72
00:04:46,965 --> 00:04:48,565
<i>I HAVE TO TELL HER</i>
<i>WHAT I FOUND OUT.</i>

73
00:04:48,565 --> 00:04:50,131
HELLO!
AAH!

74
00:04:50,131 --> 00:04:52,965
SO, YOU’RE HARUYUKI ARITA
FROM CLASS 1-C, AREN’T YOU?

75
00:04:52,965 --> 00:04:54,698
WE’RE WITH
<i>UMESATO TIMES.</i>

76
00:04:54,698 --> 00:04:56,998
THE GOSSIP COLUMN
FOR THE SCHOOL PAPER.

77
00:04:56,998 --> 00:04:57,831
WE WRITE THAT!

78
00:04:57,831 --> 00:04:59,298
OKAY,
FIRST QUESTION:

79
00:04:59,298 --> 00:05:00,698
ARE THE
RUMORS TRUE?

80
00:05:00,698 --> 00:05:02,431
ARE YOU
REALLY DATING
KUROYUKIHIME?

81
00:05:02,431 --> 00:05:03,765
AAH!
THAT’S A LIE!

82
00:05:03,765 --> 00:05:04,931
THAT’S
TOTALLY FALSE!

83
00:05:04,931 --> 00:05:06,765
BUT ACCORDING
TO OUR SOURCES,

84
00:05:06,765 --> 00:05:08,965
YOU’VE CABLE-LINKED
WITH HER TWICE IN
THE STUDENT LOUNGE.

85
00:05:08,965 --> 00:05:10,698
AND THEN ONE MORE TIME
OUTSIDE OF SCHOOL

86
00:05:10,698 --> 00:05:13,031
AT A NEARBY
COFFEE SHOP!

87
00:05:13,031 --> 00:05:18,231
YEAH. I...WAS JUST HELPING...
HER FIX HER NEURO-LINKER...

88
00:05:18,231 --> 00:05:20,465
IT’S NOTHING MORE
INTERESTING THAN THAT.

89
00:05:20,465 --> 00:05:23,065
AND THEN SHE TOOK ME
TO A COFFEE SHOP
TO SAY THANK YOU.

90
00:05:23,065 --> 00:05:24,265
THAT’S IT!

91
00:05:24,265 --> 00:05:26,665
LOOK...YOU CAN TELL
SHE DOESN’T LIKE ME

92
00:05:26,665 --> 00:05:28,765
BY THE WAY SHE ACTS
WHENEVER WE’RE TOGETHER.

93
00:05:28,765 --> 00:05:30,831
I MEAN, BY THE END
OF ALL OUR CONVERSATIONS,

94
00:05:30,831 --> 00:05:32,198
SHE’S ALWAYS
IN A BAD MOOD.

95
00:05:32,198 --> 00:05:33,698
REALLY?

96
00:05:33,698 --> 00:05:36,265
YEAH, SHE WENT AND STORMED OFF
AGAIN THIS MORNING.

97
00:05:36,265 --> 00:05:37,831
IT’S...WEIRD.

98
00:05:37,831 --> 00:05:39,631
EVERY TIME I BRING UP
CHIYU’S NAME, SHE JUST--

99
00:05:39,631 --> 00:05:41,065
CHIYURI
KURASHIMA?

100
00:05:41,065 --> 00:05:42,765
OH, RIGHT,
THAT GIRL.

101
00:05:42,765 --> 00:05:46,731
THOSE TWO GOT INTO
IT BY THE SCHOOL
GATES YESTERDAY.

102
00:05:46,731 --> 00:05:48,465
SO...
ARE WE DONE HERE?

103
00:05:48,465 --> 00:05:49,665
YEAH,
NOT QUITE.

104
00:05:49,665 --> 00:05:51,231
WE THOUGHT THE
WHOLE THING
WAS BOGUS.

105
00:05:51,231 --> 00:05:53,498
BUT NOW, I’M
NOT SO SURE
ABOUT THAT.

106
00:05:53,498 --> 00:05:55,165
HEY, ARITA.

107
00:05:55,165 --> 00:05:57,465
I THINK YOU’RE WRONG
ABOUT KUROYUKIHIME.

108
00:05:57,465 --> 00:05:58,831
SHE MIGHT
LIKE YOU
FOR REAL.

109
00:05:58,831 --> 00:05:59,698
AAH!

110
00:05:59,698 --> 00:06:01,331
I MEAN,
COME ON.

111
00:06:01,331 --> 00:06:02,965
SHE GETS MAD EACH
TIME YOU MENTION
ANOTHER GIRL’S NAME?

112
00:06:02,965 --> 00:06:04,798
THE ONLY REASON
FOR THAT...

113
00:06:04,798 --> 00:06:08,065
Both: IS BECAUSE
SHE’S JEALOUS!

114
00:06:08,065 --> 00:06:09,165
( Haru gasps )

115
00:06:11,565 --> 00:06:12,765
CAN’T BE...

116
00:06:12,765 --> 00:06:14,131
School Reporters:
<i>SHE’S JEALOUS!</i>

117
00:06:14,131 --> 00:06:15,198
THERE’S NO WAY!

118
00:06:15,198 --> 00:06:16,431
IT’S A LIE!
IT’S GOTTA BE!

119
00:06:16,431 --> 00:06:17,665
THERE’S NO WAY!

120
00:06:17,665 --> 00:06:20,431
IT JUST CAN’T!

121
00:06:20,431 --> 00:06:21,631
I DON’T GET IT.

122
00:06:21,631 --> 00:06:23,498
COME ON,
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS?

123
00:06:23,498 --> 00:06:25,131
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS TO ME?!

124
00:06:26,965 --> 00:06:28,998
<i>YOU’VE GOT EVERYTHING</i>
<i>YOU COULD EVER WANT.</i>

125
00:06:28,998 --> 00:06:32,298
<i>THE LOOKS, GRADES, POPULARITY.</i>
<i>ALL OF IT!</i>

126
00:06:32,298 --> 00:06:34,698
THERE’S NOW WAY YOU’D GO
FOR SOMEONE LIKE ME!

127
00:06:34,698 --> 00:06:36,565
<i>I’M NOT GONNA BELIEVE IT.</i>

128
00:06:36,565 --> 00:06:39,931
<i>I’M NOT GONNA GET MY HOPES UP</i>
<i>JUST TO HAVE YOU CRUSH THEM.</i>

129
00:06:39,931 --> 00:06:43,231
<i>DAMN IT.</i>
<i>WHY’D YOU HAVE TO CHOOSE ME?</i>

130
00:06:57,698 --> 00:07:01,431
( background chatter )

131
00:07:01,431 --> 00:07:03,698
HEY...

132
00:07:05,398 --> 00:07:07,431
WHY DON’T WE CHAT
WHILE WE WALK?

133
00:07:07,431 --> 00:07:09,031
SURE...

134
00:07:12,165 --> 00:07:15,965
Kuroyukihime:LISTEN.
I WANT TO APOLOGIZE
FOR THIS MORNING.

135
00:07:15,965 --> 00:07:18,165
I DON’T KNOW
WHAT CAME OVER ME.

136
00:07:18,165 --> 00:07:19,398
JUST SO YOU KNOW.

137
00:07:19,398 --> 00:07:21,698
I FOUND A CONNECTION
BETWEEN CHIYURI
AND CYAN PILE.

138
00:07:21,698 --> 00:07:23,365
HUH? REALLY?
YOU DID?

139
00:07:23,365 --> 00:07:26,265
THEN LET’S CONTINUE
THIS CONVERSATION
VIA CABLE-LINK.

140
00:07:26,265 --> 00:07:30,098
WE DON’T WANT ANYONE
EAVESDROPPING ON THE
IMPORTANT DETAILS, DO WE?

141
00:07:30,098 --> 00:07:33,465
OH...I HAD TO REPLACE
MY PREVIOUS CABLE,

142
00:07:33,465 --> 00:07:35,565
IT JUST SUDDENLY
STOPPED WORKING.

143
00:07:35,565 --> 00:07:38,965
ALL THE STORE HAD
WAS THIS SHORT ONE.

144
00:07:44,065 --> 00:07:45,865
Haru:
<i>CHIYURI’S NOT</i>
<i>CYAN PILE.</i>

145
00:07:45,865 --> 00:07:47,731
<i>SHE’S BEEN HACKED.</i>

146
00:07:47,731 --> 00:07:49,931
<i>SOMEONE SENT A VIRUS</i>
<i>TO HER NEURO-LINKER</i>
<i>AND CREATED</i>

147
00:07:49,931 --> 00:07:52,265
<i>A BACK DOOR</i>
<i>THEY COULD ACCESS.</i>
<i>( Kuroyukihime gasps )</i>

148
00:07:52,265 --> 00:07:54,465
Haru: <i>THAT’S WHY THEY’RE ABLE</i>
<i>TO LOG ONTO THE SCHOOL’S NET</i>

149
00:07:54,465 --> 00:07:58,098
<i>AND USE HER COORDINATES</i>
<i>ON CAMPUS TO CHALLENGE YOU.</i>

150
00:07:58,098 --> 00:08:00,498
Kuroyukihime:
<i>WHAT’S THE MATTER?</i>
<i>IS SOMETHING WRONG?</i>

151
00:08:00,498 --> 00:08:01,965
<i>YOU’RE ACTING STRANGE.</i>

152
00:08:01,965 --> 00:08:03,831
Haru: <i>I’M FINE.</i>
<i>DON’T WORRY ABOUT IT.</i>

153
00:08:03,831 --> 00:08:05,831
Kuroyukihime:
<i>DID SOMETHING HAPPEN</i>
<i>AT SCHOOL TODAY?</i>

154
00:08:05,831 --> 00:08:07,765
Haru: <i>I SAID</i>
<i>DON’T WORRY</i>
<i>ABOUT IT.</i>

155
00:08:07,765 --> 00:08:09,431
<i>LET’S TALK ABOUT</i>
<i>WHAT’S IMPORTANT.</i>

156
00:08:09,431 --> 00:08:11,498
<i>DO YOU HAVE ANY PROOF</i>
<i>OF THIS HACK?</i>

157
00:08:11,498 --> 00:08:14,698
<i>NO. I FIGURED THAT</i>
<i>WHOEVER IT WAS WOULD</i>
<i>NOTICE IF I DID ANYTHING.</i>

158
00:08:14,698 --> 00:08:16,165
<i>SO I LET IT BE.</i>

159
00:08:16,165 --> 00:08:17,665
Kuroyukihime:
<i>THAT’S A LOGICAL RESPONSE,</i>

160
00:08:17,665 --> 00:08:19,431
<i>BUT IT MAKES IT</i>
<i>VERY HARD TO BELIEVE.</i>

161
00:08:19,431 --> 00:08:22,431
<i>REMEMBER, BRAIN BURST</i>
<i>IS CONSIDERED AN</i>
<i>UN-HACKABLE PROGRAM.</i>

162
00:08:22,431 --> 00:08:26,731
<i>CONNECTING TO ITS MATCHING</i>
<i>SERVER THROUGH A BACKDOOR</i>
<i>IS UNHEARD OF. EVEN BY ME.</i>

163
00:08:26,731 --> 00:08:28,165
<i>SO, WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?</i>

164
00:08:28,165 --> 00:08:29,865
<i>THAT I’VE JUST</i>
<i>MADE ALL THIS UP?</i>

165
00:08:29,865 --> 00:08:31,665
<i>SOME ELABORATE LIE</i>
<i>SO I COULD SWITCH SIDES?</i>

166
00:08:31,665 --> 00:08:33,131
<i>THAT’S NOT WHAT I MEANT!</i>

167
00:08:33,131 --> 00:08:34,931
Haru: <i>WELL, IF YOU</i>
<i>DON’T BELIEVE ME,</i>

168
00:08:34,931 --> 00:08:37,165
<i>IT’S NOT REALLY ABOUT</i>
<i>THE EVIDENCE ANYMORE.</i>

169
00:08:37,165 --> 00:08:40,231
<i>LOOK, IT’S UP TO YOU</i>
<i>WHETHER YOU WANT TO</i>
<i>TRUST ME OR NOT.</i>

170
00:08:40,231 --> 00:08:43,498
Kuroyukihime:
<i>IS THAT HOW</i>
<i>YOU TRULY FEEL?</i>

171
00:08:43,498 --> 00:08:44,931
<i>JUST DO WHATEVER</i>
<i>YOU WANT.</i>

172
00:08:44,931 --> 00:08:46,465
<i>I MEAN,</i>
<i>LET’S BE HONEST.</i>

173
00:08:46,465 --> 00:08:48,198
<i>I’M NOTHING MORE</i>
<i>THAN A PAWN.</i>

174
00:08:48,198 --> 00:08:50,698
<i>A TOOL YOU CAN TOSS</i>
<i>ASIDE WHEN YOU’RE</i>
<i>DONE USING IT.</i>

175
00:08:50,698 --> 00:08:52,698
WHY WOULD YOU
SAY THAT?

176
00:08:52,698 --> 00:08:54,531
<i>YOU’RE MAD AT ME,</i>
<i>AREN’T YOU?</i>

177
00:08:54,531 --> 00:08:56,765
<i>LISTEN, THE WAY I</i>
<i>BEHAVED WAS WRONG.</i>

178
00:08:56,765 --> 00:08:59,098
<i>AND I ADMIT THAT.</i>
<i>I’M SORRY!</i>

179
00:08:59,098 --> 00:09:02,098
<i>IT’S JUST...</i>
<i>THERE ARE TIMES WHEN...</i>

180
00:09:02,098 --> 00:09:04,631
<i>WHEN I CAN’T ALWAYS</i>
<i>CONTROL MY EMOTIONS.</i>

181
00:09:04,631 --> 00:09:09,065
<i>AND IT SEEMS, ESPECIALLY</i>
<i>WHEN IT COMES TO YOU</i>
<i>AND KURASHIMA, I JUST...</i>

182
00:09:09,065 --> 00:09:10,765
<i>WHAT I’M TRYING</i>
<i>TO SAY IS...</i>

183
00:09:10,765 --> 00:09:13,498
<i>OKAY,</i>
<i>THAT’S ENOUGH.</i>
<i>HUH?</i>

184
00:09:13,498 --> 00:09:16,965
<i>THIS ISN’T JUST</i>
<i>PAINFUL TO WATCH.</i>
<i>IT’S KIND OF PATHETIC.</i>

185
00:09:16,965 --> 00:09:18,931
<i>WHAT ARE YOU</i>
<i>TALKING ABOUT?</i>

186
00:09:18,931 --> 00:09:23,531
<i>LET ME GUESS.</i>
<i>YOU HATE YOURSELF,</i>
<i>DON’T YOU?</i>

187
00:09:23,531 --> 00:09:25,765
Haru: <i>YOU’RE ONE OF THOSE</i>
<i>GIRLS WHO’S PERFECT AT</i>
<i>EVERYTHING SHE DOES,</i>

188
00:09:25,765 --> 00:09:27,198
<i>AND NOW YOU HATE</i>
<i>YOURSELF FOR IT.</i>

189
00:09:27,198 --> 00:09:29,331
<i>THAT’S WHY</i>
<i>YOU’RE DOING THIS.</i>

190
00:09:29,331 --> 00:09:32,231
<i>DEMEANING YOURSELF</i>
<i>BY PRETENDING TO LIKE</i>
<i>SOMEONE LIKE ME.</i>

191
00:09:32,231 --> 00:09:33,898
<i>I GET IT, OKAY?</i>

192
00:09:33,898 --> 00:09:36,065
<i>BUT JUST DROP THE ACT.</i>
<i>YOU DON’T NEED TO DO THIS.</i>

193
00:09:36,065 --> 00:09:38,465
<i>I’LL DO WHATEVER</i>
<i>YOU WANT ANYWAY.</i>

194
00:09:38,465 --> 00:09:40,898
<i>I DON’T NEED YOUR THANKS,</i>
<i>OR EVEN THE PRETENSE</i>
<i>THAT YOU LIKE ME.</i>

195
00:09:40,898 --> 00:09:43,965
<i>JUST TELL ME WHAT TO</i>
<i>DO, AND TOSS ME ASIDE</i>
<i>WHEN YOU’RE DONE.</i>

196
00:09:43,965 --> 00:09:46,365
<i>THAT’S THE WAY IT WORKS</i>
<i>BETWEEN PEOPLE LIKE</i>
<i>YOU AND ME.</i>

197
00:09:46,365 --> 00:09:49,798
<i>THAT’S HOW YOU</i>
<i>SHOULD TREAT ME,</i>
<i>AND YOU KNOW IT!</i>

198
00:09:52,865 --> 00:09:54,865
( sobs )
( slapping noise )

199
00:09:56,265 --> 00:09:58,065
( gasps )

200
