00:13:15,176 --> 00:13:18,242
AND ALONG THE WAY,
EVEN A FEW OF MY FRIENDS.

273
00:13:18,242 --> 00:13:24,276
BUT EVEN SOMEONE AS HIGHLY
RANKED AS ME COULD COME
NOWHERE NEAR YOUR HIGH SCORE.

274
00:13:24,276 --> 00:13:28,776
YOU’RE THE FASTEST
THERE IS, NO ONE
IS BETTER. NO ONE.

275
00:13:28,776 --> 00:13:33,242
AND I KNOW THAT SOMEDAY,
THE REST OF THE ACCELERATED
WORLD WILL KNOW THIS AS WELL,

276
00:13:33,242 --> 00:13:36,009
THAT YOU ARE THE
FASTEST LINKER
TO EVER EXIST.

277
00:13:36,009 --> 00:13:38,476
YOU WILL DEFEAT THE KINGS,
RISE UP TO THE NEXT LEVEL,

278
00:13:38,476 --> 00:13:41,142
AND DISCOVER THE TRUE
MEANING OF BRAIN BURST.

279
00:13:41,142 --> 00:13:43,976
AND BY DOING THAT, YOU WILL
UNLOCK THE TRUE POTENTIAL

280
00:13:43,976 --> 00:13:46,776
THAT LIES DEEP WITHIN
OUR MINDS AND SOULS.

281
00:13:46,776 --> 00:13:49,042
WHEN I FIRST SAW YOU
PLAYING THAT GAME,

282
00:13:49,042 --> 00:13:51,442
MY BODY TREMBLED
WITH EXCITEMENT.

283
00:13:51,442 --> 00:13:55,442
WATCHING SOMEONE BE
SO FAST AND MAGNIFICENT,
AND YET...

284
00:13:55,442 --> 00:13:58,309
