FEELINGS FINALLY WELLED
UP INSIDE ME...

292
00:14:14,942 --> 00:14:16,909
AND I REALLY
FELL FOR YOU.

293
00:14:16,909 --> 00:14:19,809
BUT I ONLY
FULLY REALIZED
THIS YESTERDAY.

294
00:14:19,809 --> 00:14:21,442
YESTERDAY?

295
00:14:21,442 --> 00:14:24,242
WHEN YOU TOLD ME ABOUT
CABLE-LINKING WITH
KURASHIMA.

296
00:14:24,242 --> 00:14:30,942
FOR THE FIRST TIME
IN MY LIFE, I WAS
JEALOUS OF SOMEONE.

297
00:14:30,942 --> 00:14:33,276
I WISH I’D REALIZED
THIS SOONER.

298
00:14:33,276 --> 00:14:35,942
BUT STILL, I HAVE BEEN
AFFORDED THIS MOMENT.

299
00:14:35,942 --> 00:14:38,176
MY CHANCE TO DECLARE
MY LOVE FOR YOU.

300
00:14:38,176 --> 00:14:41,809
I HAD HOPED THAT I WOULD
BE ABLE TO TELL YOU THIS
IN THE REAL WORLD.

301
00:14:41,809 --> 00:14:43,609
BUT NOW, MY TIME IS UP.

302
00:14:43,609 --> 00:14:44,776
( sobs )

303
