WORK HARD.
GET STRONGER
AND FASTER.

304
00:14:47,642 --> 00:14:49,109
CLIMB YOUR WAY
TO THE TOP.

305
00:14:49,109 --> 00:14:51,442
AND SEE THE WORLD
FROM THERE
IN MY PLACE.

306
00:14:51,442 --> 00:14:55,209
NO, DON’T!
YOU CAN’T
LEAVE ME LIKE THIS.

307
00:14:55,209 --> 00:14:58,509
I’M THE ONE WHO’S
SUPPOSED TO PROTECT YOU!

308
00:14:58,509 --> 00:15:00,776
BUT...
I HAVEN’T.

309
00:15:00,776 --> 00:15:06,876
I HAVEN’T DONE...
<i>ANYTHING</i> FOR YOU.

310
00:15:10,376 --> 00:15:12,376
( gasps )

311
00:15:12,376 --> 00:15:13,542
IT’S OKAY.

312
00:15:13,542 --> 00:15:15,442
I’M SURE WE’LL
MEET AGAIN SOMEDAY.

313
00:15:20,309 --> 00:15:23,309
NO! PLEASE DON’T
DO THIS! PLEASE!

314
00:15:26,509 --> 00:15:27,509
