315
00:15:27,509 --> 00:15:29,909
PHYSICAL
FULL BURST!

316
00:15:32,909 --> 00:15:34,676
( grunting )

317
00:15:43,676 --> 00:15:45,776
( gasps )
IMPOSSIBLE...

