00:15:58,242 --> 00:16:03,176
<i>OR HOW CAN A MINUTE FEEL LIKE</i>
<i>AN ETERNITY FOR TWO LOVERS WHEN</i>
<i>THEY’RE IN EACH OTHER’S ARMS?</i>

