325
00:16:11,376 --> 00:16:15,609
<i>BY ACCESSING THE NEURO-LINKER,</i>
<i>IT SPEEDS UP YOUR HEART RATE-</i>
<i>THE BASE CLOCK-</i>

326
00:16:15,609 --> 00:16:20,276
<i>A THOUSAND TIMES, AND IN</i>
<i>RETURN, IT ACCELERATES</i>
<i>YOUR THOUGHT PROCESS.</i>

327
00:16:20,276 --> 00:16:24,942
<i>ACCESSING THIS ILLICIT POWER</i>
<i>WITHIN YOUR OWN BODY</i>
<i>IS CALLED...</i>

328
00:16:24,942 --> 00:16:27,109
<i>PHYSICAL FULL BURST.</i>

329
00:16:27,109 --> 00:16:33,476
<i>HARUYUKI... WHENEVER I’M</i>
<i>WITH YOU, MY HEART IS</i>
<i>ALWAYS RACING NONSTOP.</i>

330
00:16:33,476 --> 00:16:37,076
<i>EVEN WITHOUT THE ASSISTANCE</i>
<i>OF A NEURO-LINKER</i>
<i>OR BRAIN BURST,</i>

331
00:16:37,076 --> 00:16:40,442
<i>I CONSTANTLY FELT</i>
