388
00:20:02,109 --> 00:20:05,342
<i>NO. I WON’T LET THAT HAPPEN.</i>

389
00:20:05,342 --> 00:20:06,776
<i>I’LL PROTECT YOU.</i>

390
00:20:06,776 --> 00:20:08,942
<i>I WON’T LET THIS BE THE END.</i>

391
00:20:08,942 --> 00:20:11,009
<i>THERE’S SOMETHING</i>
<i>I HAVE TO TELL HER.</i>

392
00:20:11,009 --> 00:20:13,276
